{"id": "1414460857387061278", "channel_id": "1414460857387061278", "type": 0, "author_id": "481022955472551936", "author_name": "arkismph", "author_bot": false, "content": "I got this bug twice in only 3 explorations. I've quit the game and open again but the issues remain. This's happen in chapter H4-7 and H4-12. UID:100593431 server global. This's really time consuming and frustrated.", "timestamp": "2025-09-08T04:02:27.813000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1414460858075189378", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1362613, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1414460857387061278/1414460858075189378/image.png?ex=69ff5a93&is=69fe0913&hm=361dd3c7bd5e33d57218a779f5c35fa172607fbc51277c108519c617a06199a2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414460857387061278", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Bug report!!!!", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1414555526456541195", "channel_id": "1414555526456541195", "type": 0, "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "author_bot": false, "content": "It’s not even a visual bug, the entire menu is gone and only comes back after closing and re-opening the game. I play on IOS.", "timestamp": "2025-09-08T10:18:38.678000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1414555527387680778", "filename": "IMG_6108.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1134824, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1414555526456541195/1414555527387680778/IMG_6108.png?ex=69ff09fe&is=69fdb87e&hm=7a29f011f50c68e0f6acb1c4065b5c4f0aafb4fe3b6219119ee23c8a1b1c0591&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414555526456541195", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Weekly trials menu disappears after playing a match/ being in queue for a few seconds", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1414669096422739999", "channel_id": "1414669096422739999", "type": 0, "author_id": "244028747999608832", "author_name": "vxvendetta", "author_bot": false, "content": "A thing I heard a lot of people say is that the first battle of Dtide is very hard (because you don't have resources to start, more relics etc) and then, if you can survive it, the rest can be more manageable.\nWouldn't be possible to, potentially, reduce the strength of the very first encounter by around 25\\20% (as in stats or even composition)? \nTo give teams that maybe struggle more right at start, a better chance to build up and play the level?\nIf that is too easy one can increase the difficulty of the general stage slightly to compensate, but maybe that can increase the potential variety of usable teams, or at least alleviate the initial frustration from that first fight.\nWhat is **Your Opinion?**", "timestamp": "2025-09-08T17:49:55.868000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-08T17:51:22.071000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1414669096968257536", "filename": "UI_Events_Bg_Tawil02.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 1070966, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1414669096422739999/1414669096968257536/UI_Events_Bg_Tawil02.png?ex=69ff73c3&is=69fe2243&hm=b3798ca647eb17179c5b2c08c946c15fe3751bc4d5a0522a59c324b10b515211&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414669096422739999", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Potential changes and opinions for Dtide", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1414472594161139802", "channel_id": "1414472594161139802", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2025-09-08T04:49:06.078000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1414472594350149703", "filename": "Screenshot_20250908_124525_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 207139, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1414472594161139802/1414472594350149703/Screenshot_20250908_124525_Morimens.jpg?ex=69ff6582&is=69fe1402&hm=000a307d65d43ccc83a5c0800bdc016d4a57b12d589e9d2253326b61d4a4675c&"}, {"id": "1414472594714787850", "filename": "Screenshot_20250908_124529_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 201368, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1414472594161139802/1414472594714787850/Screenshot_20250908_124529_Morimens.jpg?ex=69ff6582&is=69fe1402&hm=e8cbad530b0cf1ec53b09bff4f7b301bd93930a6d6ef322d54ce3f44f5b25d3a&"}, {"id": "1414472595096735764", "filename": "Screenshot_20250908_124540_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 141343, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1414472594161139802/1414472595096735764/Screenshot_20250908_124540_Morimens.jpg?ex=69ff6582&is=69fe1402&hm=c4d30b2041efee482a0650b3ae82afd4fd4a60bb190b9b46534e628693e8b718&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414472594161139802", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「处理中」相位bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1414593722888360120", "channel_id": "1414593722888360120", "type": 0, "author_id": "1403431686116741143", "author_name": "2300011747", "author_bot": false, "content": "接触这个游戏也有一段时间了，这一段时间的游玩体验还是比较不错的。但是有一点还是让我觉得有点难受，就是有些角色的某个启灵乃至超限爆发机制过于特殊，导致是否拥有这个启灵/超限爆发让拥有这个角色的体验完全两极分化，特别是有些角色可能没有拿到关键启灵就完全上不了场。而融灾又考察玩家的BOX深度，可能你的低启角色完全没有环境上场。希望之后的角色设计可以不要将角色的关键机制拆分到启灵之中（比如<减费>和<保留>这种比较重要的机制），而是更多地将数值部分的内容添加到启灵中去。当然超限爆发需要一些特殊机制也是无可厚非的，但是不要像塔薇和熔朵那样过于依赖超限爆发。这样做一方面照顾到了新手玩家的抽卡压力，另一方面让愿意投入资源抽卡的玩家也能够看到自己的投入转化为实打实的提升。\n    我还是希望忘却前夜能够更加长久而稳定地运营下去，给更多卡牌爱好者们带来乐趣。希望策划可以稍微考虑一下我的建议，谢谢。<:agree:1400771815076528258>", "timestamp": "2025-09-08T12:50:25.417000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414593722888360120", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "新人对这个游戏的一点看法与建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1414555908234809386", "channel_id": "1414555908234809386", "type": 0, "author_id": "658320022359375882", "author_name": "vaerre", "author_bot": false, "content": "求改善皮克曼2算力卡【绘影摹形】的说明，只留【下回合开始】\n刚开始读说明时挺困惑的<:processing:1357185814567718963>", "timestamp": "2025-09-08T10:20:09.701000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1414555908503240704", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 311926, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1414555908234809386/1414555908503240704/image.png?ex=69ff0a59&is=69fdb8d9&hm=b68c698a1f40ca2a8267b5b0d9a3f3aa9920744717b6ec858ead8156c2a3e4fc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1414555908234809386", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」皮克曼【绘影摹形】说明", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
